      • download

        public static void download(String saveFileName,
            InputStream inputStream,
            Number contentLength,
            HttpServletRequest request,
            HttpServletResponse response)
        下载(以 contentType=application/force-download) 强制下载.
        Parameters:
        saveFileName - 保存文件的文件名,将会被设置到 Content-Disposition header 中
        inputStream - 保存数据输入流
        contentLength - 如果是网络流就需要自己来取到大小了,比如

        HttpURLConnection httpconn = (HttpURLConnection)url.openConnection();
        httpconn.getContentLength(); 

        InputStream.available() 不使用于网络情况
        request - 用来获取request相关信息 ,仅用来记录log
        response - response
        See Also:
        IOWriteUtil.write(InputStream, OutputStream), "org.springframework.http.MediaType"
